{
  "widgets": [

    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 24, "height": 3,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "# 🚀 URL Shortener — Production NOC Dashboard\n**Environment:** Production &nbsp;|&nbsp; **Region:** us-east-1 &nbsp;|&nbsp; **Stack:** Nginx → Node.js → MySQL/MongoDB\n\n> 🟢 **Web Tier** `i-0b377383592c91dea` &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 🗄️ **DB Tier** `i-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX` &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 📡 **Agent:** CloudWatch Agent Active\n\n---"
      }
    },

    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0, "y": 3, "width": 24, "height": 2,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "### 🔔 Alarm Status\n> ℹ️ To enable live alarm status here: create CloudWatch Alarms for CPU/Memory/Disk thresholds, then replace this widget with an `alarm` type widget referencing their ARNs. &nbsp;|&nbsp; **Quick links:** [Create Alarm](https://us-east-1.console.aws.amazon.com/cloudwatch/home?region=us-east-1#alarmsV2:create) &nbsp;|&nbsp; [View All Alarms](https://us-east-1.console.aws.amazon.com/cloudwatch/home?region=us-east-1#alarmsV2:)"
      }
    },

    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0, "y": 5, "width": 24, "height": 1,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "## 🌐 Web & API Tier — Nginx / Node.js"
      }
    },

    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0, "y": 6, "width": 6, "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "⚡ Web CPU Utilization",
        "metrics": [
          [ "AWS/EC2", "CPUUtilization", "InstanceId", "i-0b377383592c91dea", { "color": "#1f77b4", "label": "CPU %" } ]
        ],
        "view": "gauge",
        "region": "us-east-1",
        "stat": "Average",
        "period": 60,
        "yAxis": { "left": { "min": 0, "max": 100 } },
        "annotations": {
          "horizontal": [
            { "color": "#ff7f0e", "label": "Warning (70%)", "value": 70 },
            { "color": "#d62728", "label": "Critical (90%)", "value": 90, "fill": "above" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 6, "y": 6, "width": 6, "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "🧠 Web Memory Utilization",
        "metrics": [
          [ { "expression": "SEARCH('Namespace=\"CWAgent\" MetricName=\"mem_used_percent\" InstanceId=\"i-0b377383592c91dea\"', 'Average', 60)", "id": "w_mem", "color": "#9467bd", "label": "Memory %" } ]
        ],
        "view": "gauge",
        "region": "us-east-1",
        "yAxis": { "left": { "min": 0, "max": 100 } },
        "annotations": {
          "horizontal": [
            { "color": "#ff7f0e", "label": "Warning (75%)", "value": 75 },
            { "color": "#d62728", "label": "Critical (90%)", "value": 90, "fill": "above" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 12, "y": 6, "width": 6, "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "💾 Web Disk Usage (Root)",
        "metrics": [
          [ { "expression": "SEARCH('Namespace=\"CWAgent\" MetricName=\"disk_used_percent\" InstanceId=\"i-0b377383592c91dea\" path=\"/\"', 'Average', 60)", "id": "w_disk", "color": "#2ca02c", "label": "Disk %" } ]
        ],
        "view": "gauge",
        "region": "us-east-1",
        "yAxis": { "left": { "min": 0, "max": 100 } },
        "annotations": {
          "horizontal": [
            { "color": "#ff7f0e", "label": "Warning (80%)", "value": 80 },
            { "color": "#d62728", "label": "Critical (90%)", "value": 90, "fill": "above" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 18, "y": 6, "width": 6, "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "📶 Web Network Traffic",
        "metrics": [
          [ "AWS/EC2", "NetworkIn",  "InstanceId", "i-0b377383592c91dea", { "color": "#1f77b4", "label": "Bytes In" } ],
          [ ".",        "NetworkOut", ".",           ".",                   { "color": "#2ca02c", "label": "Bytes Out" } ]
        ],
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stacked": false,
        "region": "us-east-1",
        "stat": "Average",
        "period": 60,
        "legend": { "position": "bottom" }
      }
    },

    {
